      "start": 113.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 118.41999816894531,
      "text": "You know I'm good for it, good for it, good for it",
      "start": 115.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 121.31999969482422,
      "text": "Pockets, pockets, pockets, thank you for the money",
      "start": 118.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 123.68000030517578,
      "text": "I don't even know if you even understand",
      "start": 121.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 126.81999969482422,
      "text": "I gave you so much lies, you brought some motherfucker in the hand",
      "start": 123.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 129.02000427246094,
      "text": "And the man doesn't understand",
      "start": 126.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 130.89999389648438,
      "text": "It's just a game, man",
      "start": 129.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 133.17999267578125,
      "text": "A game where you take it over",
      "start": 131.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 134.9600067138672,
      "text": "Fuckin' like a first street motherfucker",
      "start": 133.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 138.32000732421875,
      "text": "We touch down next time, next time you'll think",
